## Introdução


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(tidyverse)
x <- rnorm(n = 40)
y <- 1.5*x + rnorm(0, 2, n = 40)
d <- data.frame(x,y)
d %>% ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) + geom_point() + theme_bw()
```
